{"tid":2361912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色經濟圈2020回顧｜美心蝕4億　富臨被追租　藍店改頭換面博重新出發","createTime":"2021-01-11T05:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T07:12:11.000Z","uid":271829,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f643697084a3d446db037ec539e0e488267a3c13","tid":2361912,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T05:38:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x9sf6q7GHsw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dx9sf6q7GHsw&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7Qx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=6213f710\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x9sf6q7GHsw</a><br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n最大型飲食集團之一的美心，其創辦人伍沾德的長女伍淑清於聯合國人權會議上的出位言論，加上一句「放棄年輕人」，這樣反客為主的言辭，令美心成為重點抵制對象之一。就算美心屢次發聲明指伍淑清沒有於公司擔任任何職位，沒有參與管理，也無法改變美心旗下店舖成為抵制對象的局面。美心旗下的食肆美心皇宮，今年年初曾經傳出裁員，當時被「裝修」令集團要承受大筆維修費，因此選擇在部份店舖租約完結之後，不再續約。而今年5月，集團亦疑大裁員超過100人。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_771620_0/黃色經濟圈2020回顧-美心蝕4億-富臨被追租-藍店改頭換面搏重新出發\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_771620_0%2F%E9%BB%83%E8%89%B2%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%9C%882020%E5%9B%9E%E9%A1%A7-%E7%BE%8E%E5%BF%83%E8%9D%954%E5%84%84-%E5%AF%8C%E8%87%A8%E8%A2%AB%E8%BF%BD%E7%A7%9F-%E8%97%8D%E5%BA%97%E6%94%B9%E9%A0%AD%E6%8F%9B%E9%9D%A2%E6%90%8F%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E5%87%BA%E7%99%BC&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7Qx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=9d059e28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_771620_0%2F%E9%BB%83%E8%89%B2%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%9C%882020%E5%9B%9E%E9%A1%A7-%E7%BE%8E%E5%BF%83%E8%9D%954%E5%84%84-%E5%AF%8C%E8%87%A8%E8%A2%AB%E8%BF%BD%E7%A7%9F-%E8%97%8D%E5%BA%97%E6%94%B9%E9%A0%AD%E6%8F%9B%E9%9D%A2%E6%90%8F%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E5%87%BA%E7%99%BC&h=0b3a4127\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_771620_0/黃色經濟圈2020回顧-美心蝕4億-富臨被追租-藍店改頭換面搏重新出發</a>"},{"pid":"9f1eb2c5f7eb0b9a0586d4948928646c26e25bfe","tid":2361912,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco